    I think this was my first TikTok? (Note: the page has now been privated)

    <br>

    <video controls src="https://homecdn.frii.site/v0f044gc0000cjbtl83c77u1m4mu65ag.MP4" />
    The battery exploded when I accidentally stabbed it with a screwdriver
</details>

<br>


When I was putting the phone back together in August of 2023, I managed to stab the battery with my screwdriver. Of course the battery broke, and the phone was rendered useless.
I decided to buy a new battery for it in September, and made it work again. 

<br>

I didn't really have a use for the phone until the summer of 2024, when I asked my parents if I could setup it as a server, and run Pi-hole on it. They agreed, and I set it up as a server.
Since I didn't actually have root perms on the phone, I couldn't do much else with the phone. Unfortunately, my parents decided to force me to take the "server" down a few months after.

<br>

I absolutely shattered my iPhone 12 Pro in May of 2025, and had to use the Xiaomi while my real phone was being worked on. The only positive thing about the experience was Google's keyboard.

